<p>Multi-unit buildings in Beverly Hills often have building management, HOA rules, and concierge protocols. We coordinate with building staff, work within noise windows, and keep laundry rooms clean during and after every repair — shoe covers in luxury homes, thorough cleanup before we leave. We call ahead to confirm arrival time and provide preparation instructions specific to your LG model so you're ready when we arrive. If your building requires technician registration or insurance documentation, call us before scheduling and we'll provide what's needed. We don't need to be walked through procedures twice.</p>

